AppRecommender - Application recommender for GNU/Linux systems
---------------------------------------------------------------

Install dependencies
---------------------

# apt-get install \
python python-xapian python-apt python-cluster python-webpy python-simplejson \
python-numpy apt-xapian-index app-install-data python-xdg


Run AppRecommender web UI
--------------------------

# cd ./src/web
# ./server.py

Open a browser and access http://localhost:8080


More info at https://github.com/tassia/AppRecommender/wiki


Run AppRecommender in Terminal
------------------------------

- Into folder /vagrant/ create the folder .app-recommender/ if this folder not exists

- Into folder .app-recommender/ create the folder filters/ if this folder not exists

- Into folder /vagrant/src/bin/ run the following command:

- - $ ./get_tags.sh > ../../.app-recommender/filters/debtags

- - $ ./get_axipkgs.py > ../../.app-recommender/filters/desktopapps

- - $ ./indexer_axi.py sample ../../.app-recommender/filters/desktopapps
